ival, Escape, and Annihilation. Encounter dozens of enemy styles, randomized upgrade paths, and fresh challenges in every mission. Unleash your inner space warrior and join the action in \"EON Fighter\"!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146720/extras/29793f2c8149e717315375f251af9176.poster.avif?t=1758817497\" width=610 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146720/extras/29793f2c8149e717315375f251af9176.webm?t=1758817497\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146720/extras/29793f2c8149e717315375f251af9176.mp4?t=1758817497\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
